---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Security News & Resources
description: The latest cybersecurity news and advisories from CISA, The Hacker News, BleepingComputer, and Krebs on Security — curated weekly by IronGate.
permalink: /resources/
ctaHeading: "Worried about a headline you just read?"
ctaSub: "Book a free 30-minute consult and we'll tell you honestly whether it affects your firm."
---

<section class="section" style="padding-bottom:40px; background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--mist-50),#fff); text-align:center;" aria-label="Resources overview">
  <span class="pill">Resources</span>
  <h1 class="display-1" style="max-width:820px; margin:18px auto 0;">Security news &amp; guidance</h1>
  <p class="lead" style="max-width:640px; margin:20px auto 0;">What's happening in cybersecurity right now &mdash; advisories and reporting from the sources we trust, refreshed every week. Headlines link to the original articles.</p>
</section>

<section class="section" style="padding-top:32px" aria-label="Latest security headlines">
  <div class="grid-3">
    {% for item in news %}
    <article class="news-card">
      <div class="news-card__thumb news-card__thumb--{{ item.slug }}" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="news-card__wordmark">{{ item.source }}<span>.</span></div>
        <div class="news-card__tagline">{{ item.tagline }}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="news-card__body">
        <div class="news-card__date"><time datetime="{{ item.date | isoDate }}">{{ item.date | newsDate }}</time> &middot; {{ item.source }}</div>
        <h3><a href="{{ item.link }}" rel="noopener external" target="_blank">{{ item.title }}<span style="position:absolute;width:1px;height:1px;overflow:hidden;clip:rect(0 0 0 0);"> (opens in a new tab)</span></a></h3>
      </div>
    </article>
    {% else %}
    <p style="color:var(--slate-500)">Fresh security headlines are being gathered &mdash; check back shortly.</p>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
  <p style="text-align:center; font-size:14px; color:var(--slate-500); margin-top:40px;">Sources: CISA advisories, The Hacker News, BleepingComputer, and Krebs on Security. IronGate curates but does not author these articles.</p>
</section>

{% include "partials/cta.njk" %}
